1. *Prokleti* čovek se brzo obogatio preko sumnjivih poslova. (The cursed man quickly became wealthy through suspicious deals.)
2. Njegov *prokleti* svet je izgleda na ivici raspada. (His cursed world is apparently on the brink of collapse.)
3. *Prokletstvo* se nastavlja na naredno pokoljenje. (The curse continues to the next generation.)
4. Njeno *prokletstvo* je preraslo u legendu. (Her curse has grown into a legend.)
5. Oni su primorani da žive pod *prokletstvom*. (They are forced to live under a curse.)